Team Achievements: Australia posted their fifth win in seven matches and are third in the standings.
England slumped to their sixth defeat in seven matches and remain rooted to the bottom of the table.
Post-Match Reflections: Jos Buttler expressed disappointment over England's premature exit from the World Cup.
Pat Cummins highlighted the team's brilliant performance and noted that they haven't played their complete game yet.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played at the Narendra Modi Stadium in Ahmedabad, India.
The result impacted England's World Cup campaign and their morale ahead of the tournament.
